\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Isut â, Sises K ârai poitor â, Isens akon n…®r…® win…®paino,\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Ma'siu 13:55; Ma' 6:3\x* 
\p Kamoro ik…®'masa' kon, Papa Ik âip ân â ni'n ânka'san, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Sises K ârai n âpa'sima'san enakan: 
\p  
\v 2 Usentu'man n…®to', t âusewankamai' p âra e'n…®to', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® usi'n ânkan n…®to' nesii …®iwano' kon pe miyar…® r…®. 
\s1 Papa Uya Tasa' Pen N…® Aw…®r…® Te'san Makooi M…®r…® Awonsi'k…® To' Uma'tato' 
\p  
\v 3 Utonpa ton n â'kw…®, …®menukapai'nokon esa' e'tane, ina nekaman â epika't…®n n…®to' ekareei p…®', …®menukato' kon pe uya kuru e'kup â'p â m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ipan pe kuru …®yekama'po kon pe apur…®to' K âri'san pe e'n…® p…®' wenai …®yetok â kon pa Papa n ât âr â'p â tikin nan par…® r…®, t âusensimaton pe p âra r…® wak â ton ena'.  
\v 4 Ap âne p âra pena r…® to' eno'mato' p…®' iye'menukasa' r â'san t âron kon ka'pon am â' ewonsa' man ama'ai …®'koro'ta'nokon. Papa uya tasa' pen n…® aw…®r…® te'san ka'pon am â', Papa, itese' p…®' e'n…®to' uya wak â nonkasa' ensimanin n â'san makoi eseru ya', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Sises K ârai tikin nan n…® r…®ken eke, uyepuru kon t ânonkai'.\f + \fr 1:4 \ft T âron n…® ton imenukasa' uya, \fq p âsamoro ennakanin nan ti'sa am â' esi usensiman i'se makoi yau uko'man n…®to' ya', Sises r…® apur…®to' uya'nokon nonka uya'nokon i'se to' esi, \ft ta.\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Tanporo ser…® ton i'tusa' auya'nokon e'tane, …®yemiya'pont…®pai'nokon esi Itepuru\f + \fr 1:5 \fq Itepuru, \ft m…®r…® pe p âra \fq Sises\f* uya t âmunk…® am â' enpa'ka'p â Isi' apai, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® apur…®nin nan pen to' koro'tau te'san ma'tan âk â'p â iya.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt E'sotas 12:51; Nonpa 14:29-30\x* 
\v 6 Inser â am â' n…®r…® kanan, eke pe te'to' kon yau enkurunpaino kon pen e'tane t âpata'se' kon nonkanin n â'san p…®' …®yemiya'pont…® uya 'nokon‚Äîp âsamoro ku'sa' iya ewarup…® yau a'sisa' pe inke r…® eseru wann…® aimenkato' Weyu pona r…®.  
\v 7 M…®r…® kasa r…® Satan m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Komora m…®r…® awonsi'k…® pata ton ipiyawo'nan yawon kon e't âr â'p â ekuman m…®r…® awonsi'k…® n…®k…® eseru ya'. Apo' inkero' ke ekota'man n…®to' ento' ip…®' pe to' esi'p â.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Iseneses 19:1-24\x* 
\p  
\v 8 M…®r…® na'ne' kasa kuru r…® mar…®, p âsamoro te'ne'p…®'san uya t âpun kon ma'tan âk â, merunt…® tentaino kon pe te'sen nurunpa, inser â am â' sapema r…® n…®r…®.  
\v 9 E'tane Maikar â, inser â am â' epuru tonpa e'maimu'p…®t â a'tai Makoi a'k…®r…®, Mosi' ekepu wenai isapema i'se iyesi'p â pen e'tane, ‚ÄúT…®w…® Itepuru …®yeseremek âi!‚Äù ta'p â iya.\x - \xo 1:9 \xt Taniyer â 10:13, 21; 12:1; Isenpoikasa' 12:7; Isu'taronomi 34:6; Sakaraya 3:2\x* 
\v 10 E'tane r…® p âsamoro ka'pon am â' usaurok â t ânto'ka'n âk ân â kon pen n…® t âsapemai'; to' n âto'ka'n âk ân â t âpe'nokon, o' am â' t âusenuminkasan pen kasa‚Äîser…® …®ri ton uya kuru to' ma'tan âk â m…®r…®. 
\p  
\v 11 ∆ós…® yau to' esi! Keen e'ma r â'p â an ânsa' to' uya man; to' ut…®sa' man t âneporon â kon epose'na Peran utano'ma'p â ya' kasa r…® mar…®; to' uma'tasa' man tiwano' pe e'pai Kora esi'p â ya'.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Iseneses 4:3-8; Nonpa 22:1-35; 16:1-35\x* 
\p  
\v 12 P âsamoro esi …®ri pe iteseru usi'n ânkan pe usewe'n…®to' yau, enta'nan p…®' aya'k…®r…®'nokon, mara r â'kw…® r…® to' …®piy…®'to' p âra r…®‚Äîkarimeru am â' pa'simanin nan tiwano' kon pe t âuta're't…®san pe r…® to' esi. Kapuru' tuna a'k…®ron pen pe r…® to' esi, a'setun n âposi'man â; w âi a'taino y âi ton, iteperu p ânon, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® ikuru'kasa'‚Äîasa' ite'kwa ima'tasa' pe to' esi.  
\v 13 Parau pon …®s…® sipa'sipa pe to' esi, to' …®piy…®'to' a'koronta; sirik…® am â' t âutano'ma kon pe t âupininsan, to' iwano' pe ipan n…® ewarup…® ekonekasa' t…®w…®ro' pe r…®. 
\p  
\v 14 Iino', Atan awonsi'k…® 7 pe iku'nin\f + \fr 1:14 \fq 7 pe iku'nin: \ft Ser…® itu'kanoro na'ne' esi Atan awonsi'k…® Iino' p â'k â pona 7 pe iu't…®sa' to' tamokori ton pe'ne.\f* usaurok â'p â pu'kena' pe p âsamoro p…®': ‚ÄúAp âne ent…®', Itepuru uye'n…® p…®' man 1,000 kaisaron kon pona r…® 1,000 kaisaron kon, tu'kan kon wak â ton tiwano' ton pokon pe\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Iseneses 5:18, 21-24\x* 
\v 15 tanporon kon eseru aimenkase'na, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® Papa uya tasa' pen n…® aw…®r…® te'san eno'mase'na, Papa uya tasa' pen n…® aw…®r…® te'san n âkup â'p â Papa uya tasa' pen n…® aw…®r…® te'san eseru yau, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® tanporon n…® …®s…® pe Papa uya tasa' pen n…® aw…®r…® te'san t âmakooikena' nan usauro'sa' r â'p â ewa'noma pe,‚Äù ta'p â iya.\f + \fr 1:15 \ft Ser…® panton esi Esuwer â am â' pantom â Iino' p…®', m…®r…®pan p âra iyesi Penaro' Ekonekan n…®to' yau.\f* 
\v 16 P âsamoro ka'pon am â' esi tentarunsan, …®ri …®nenpaino kon n…®ken; i'se te'to' kon makoi eseru poro t âut…®san; t âp…®'nokon n…® t âutapur…®san m…®r…® awonsi'k…® t âron kon p…®' wak â pe itese' t âusauro'san wak â epoto' pe t âuya'nokon. 
\s1 Panaman M…®r…® Awonsi'k…® Enupan 
\p  
\v 17 E'tane, utonpa ton n â'kw…®, …®yenu kon yau iku't…®' uyepuru kon Sises K ârai nennoko'san nekama'p â r â'p â.  
\v 18 Ta'p â to' uya …®p…®'nokon, ‚ÄúIweyu u'mat â a'tai, sapeman pe t âuta'k…®r…®san e'to' oton, …®ri eseru i'se te'to' kon aw…®r…® te'san,‚Äù\x - \xo 1:18 \xt 2 Pi'ta 3:3\x* tawon.  
\v 19 P âsamoro kamoro ka'pon am â' ata'n â'nin kon, t âpun kon eseru aw…®ron kon Iya'kwar â esanon pen. 
\p  
\v 20 E'tane, …®m…®r…®'nokon, utonpa ton n â'kw…®, wak â kuru apur…®to' auya'nokon yau e'ka't…®', m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®p âremat…®' Wak â A'kwar â eseru yau.  
\v 21 Papa usi'n ânkato' yau e't…®', uyepuru kon Sises K ârai usentu'mato' enup…®k…®r…® …®wesi kon koro'tau, miyar…® r…® …®uko'manto' kon ya' ayase'na'nokon t âuye'sen. 
\p  
\v 22 Ikasimanin nan p…®' t âusentu'mai' e't…®';  
\v 23 t âron kon imo'kat…®' apo' apai, to' pika't…® pe; t âron kon p…®' …®usentu'mato' kon enpoikat…®', enari'n ân n…® pokon pe t âsumai'‚Äî…®ri iteseru ton ke to' na'sik â'p â to' pon ewaruma't…®i'ma. 
\s1 Papa Apur…®p…®'to' 
\p  
\v 24 M…®r…® awonsi'k…® ser…® si, tanporo eke pe iku'to' nesii Papa iwano' pe, …®ye'pi'po namai' …®ku'nin, ayaton a'kwa pe te'to' ya', t âmakooikenan pe p âra m…®r…® awonsi'k…® eke pe r…® pori' pokon pe.  
\v 25 Tanporo eke pe iku'to' nesii itiwano' pe, k âr…® r…® r…®ken Papa upika't…®nin kon, Sises K ârai uyepuru kon poro. Ewai', eke pe iku'to', eke pe iye'to' yau imerunt…®r â, ipana'pano, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® merunt…® esi itiwano' pe, it…®piya yau r…®, ser…® pe na'ne' m…®r…® awonsi'k…® siyaro' r…®! Amen.